description:
Master Charger  Discography 2010-2016 320ak

This celebrates the return after a five year absence of recording from Master Charger. Not only does the new album mark their return it also shows the band in a different light. Master Charger are simply Re-Charged and ready to hit the road in support of thier "Eroding Empires" release. 

Master Charger A Three piece unit conceived in the blackest heart of Nottinghamshire, England.
Engineered and Recorded by Michael Ranzetta. Produced by Master Charger. Artwork by Barla Horn.
